Invocation Name: twin lead loss
des: Twin Lead has fallen out of favor in the ham radio world. Coax is far less affected by the environment in which it is used. However, you may be surprised at how low twin lead losses are. All losses are approximations. Loss figures are taken from www.rfcafe.com. Thanks to Kirt Blattenberger.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
